You warned me. You told me what was coming to the nations. All that we say in word and deed we give all to the glory of God.

01:57:57.120 --> 01:58:01.399
We attract and deflect. We know apart from him I can do nothing.

01:58:01.400 --> 01:58:10.979
I'm so thankful. I'm in awe. You know I'm in awe of everything he has showed us tonight.

01:58:10.980 --> 01:58:21.673
Again, things that I can say and things that I can't. But I'm so thankful for the Holy Spirit to lead us into truth.

01:58:21.674 --> 01:58:30.559
And I'm in awe of what he's done. He's such a good God. He warns his people to pray.

01:58:30.560 --> 01:58:37.771
So, thank you for coming out praying with us. We love you. Remember, there's 4,600 of you.

01:58:37.772 --> 01:58:45.209
We got a lot of work done. And so we're so grateful for the people that took the time tonight.

01:58:45.210 --> 01:58:50.123
It's getting really late. And I need to eat. I'm doing really well.

01:58:50.124 --> 01:58:57.654
I'm trying really hard to eat right. So all to the glory of God for two hours now.

01:58:57.655 --> 01:59:02.560
So long videos for you to watch, but I know it was all led by the Holy Spirit.

01:59:02.561 --> 01:59:10.639
And I pray it blesses you. We'll be back and pray again. There's something about to happen.

01:59:10.640 --> 01:59:24.640
So, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again soon. Bye bye.

